title: Somebody Has To Eat The Smelliest Fruit! + We Talk With A Guy Going To Space + Bobby’s Mailbag: How To Deal With A Creepy Neighbor
itunes:title: Somebody Has To Eat The Smelliest Fruit! + We Talk With A Guy Going To Space + Bobby’s Mailbag: How To Deal With A Creepy Neighbor
description:
We spin the wheel and the loser has to eat a Durian...aka the world’s smelliest fruit. We talk to Chris Sembroski who is part of the St. Jude all-civilian mission to space. Bobby asks him about his training and if they are telling him if it’s safe. In Bobby’s mailbag, a listener has a situation with a potentially creeping neighbor spying on their daughter.
